description:
Re-write your legend through verse and blood, and bring respite to the tragic youth of Kalevala by besting mythical creatures, monsters, spirits - and even Life and Death themselves - in battle.

Perform rituals, navigate treacherous lands, and learn from every misstep to become stronger.

Get roused by:
- Arming up with different weapons, artifacts and poems to craft the perfect build;
- Learning the story of your characters, through besting challenging trials;
- Testing your mettle against epic, old school boss encounters;
- Bits and pieces of genuine finno-karelian legends;
- The dynamic and intense dungeon synth OST!
